{"tid":1928801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國迎新好A！胸部倒煉乳 逼男生舔男生乳頭","createTime":"2020-03-16T14:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T16:20:25.000Z","uid":3189,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"455c52fd36bd12f533930ac7e607eea23d0f9b6c","tid":1928801,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/naagHXaOf4B5aYMa6QpmVw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NDA1/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/kairos.tw/5e937a09f3791dea338a4ce19692aa6f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnaagHXaOf4B5aYMa6QpmVw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NDA1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fkairos.tw%2F5e937a09f3791dea338a4ce19692aa6f&h=23d10d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球大學迎新會花招百出，且越玩越過分，不是充滿凌辱就是帶有色情意味，而重視學長學弟制的泰國學校，其迎新會更是誇張。過去有爆出有學姊逼迫變性新生當眾「脫上衣」、或者規定不認識的男女新生互相親吻以「快速增進感情。日前泰國瑪哈沙拉堪大學（มหาวิทยาลัยมหาสารคาม）爆出疑似迎新時，餵新生吃屎的事件後，後來又傳出該大學另一段迎新影片，學長學弟躺在地上互抓鳥，還讓男同學舔倒在奶頭上的煉乳，超A行為引起校方關注。<br />\n<br />\n據泰國《matichon》報導，臉書粉絲團「Anti SOTUS」分享了一段大學迎新的影片，從影片中可看到，眾學長學弟脫去上衣平躺在地，除了將手放在隔壁同學的下體上外，還在胸部地方倒煉乳，然後讓他人來舔。只見舔煉乳的男同學尷尬的笑著，被舔的學生表情木訥，其他學生則站在前方嘻笑著。<br />\n<br />\n影片流出後，有網友留言說「雖然我已經大學畢業了，但我還是不喜歡這種活動」、「校方應該要對這種事情負起責任」。瑪哈沙拉堪大學16日在臉書發文指出，已經從各方得知此項消息，將做進一步的調查，如果情況屬實，將一切按照規定對學生進行懲處。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，泰國的學校非常重視學長學弟制度，會為剛入學的新生舉辦迎新活動，希望他們能迅速和高年級學生建立關係，及早適應學園生活。但這些迎新活動往往玩得太過份，讓新生心中留下陰影，校方應訂下相關規範，避免學生玩過火。（吳雯淇／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E8%BF%8E%E6%96%B0%E5%A5%BDa-%E8%83%B8%E9%83%A8%E5%80%92%E7%85%89%E4%B9%B3-%E9%80%BC%E7%94%B7%E8%88%94%E7%94%B7%E4%B9%B3%E9%A0%AD-030244077.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25BF%258E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A5%25BDa-%25E8%2583%25B8%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2580%2592%25E7%2585%2589%25E4%25B9%25B3-%25E9%2580%25BC%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%2588%2594%25E7%2594%25B7%25E4%25B9%25B3%25E9%25A0%25AD-030244077.html&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=c30aa40d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E8%BF%8E%E6%96%B0%E5%A5%BDa-%E8%83%B8%E9%83%A8%E5%80%92%E7%85%89%E4%B9%B3-%E9%80%BC%E7%94%B7%E8%88%94%E7%94%B7%E4%B9%B3%E9%A0%AD-030244077.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wP9tnMG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwP9tnMG.gif&h=be942de7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ef4e3b24c05d3b102c98f672df227ea8d1d363a","tid":1928801,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:56:14.000Z","msg":"咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea393e1db89f241e2193ac0793c96fffcd733f1","tid":1928801,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:59:26.000Z","msg":"Gay"},{"pid":"8d1bcb90444a1852464fae217850ecd0b6ce64a1","tid":1928801,"uid":155246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb0431bb682fcd9d601d5b09069f6b6891842ea","tid":1928801,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T15:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e878c6ac3da036d6c234813fc859c704ad688ed8","tid":1928801,"uid":2